<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Sherubtse College Feedback System</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .navbar {
      background-color: #003366;
    }

    .navbar-brand,
    .nav-link,
    .btn-logout {
      color: #fff !important;
    }

    .navbar-nav .nav-link {
      color: white;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
      color: #ffcc00 !important; /* bright yellow or choose your preferred color */
    }

    .btn-logout {
      color: white;
      border-color: white;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn-logout:hover {
      background-color: #dc3545 !important; /* Bootstrap red */
      color: white !important;
      border-color: #dc3545 !important;
    }


    .hero {
      background-image: url('/images/bg.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
      padding: 100px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .highlight-box {
      border: 2px solid #cc0000;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .emoji {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .feature-btn {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-btn.start {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
    }

    .feature-btn.start:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    .feature-btn.view {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
    }

    .feature-btn.view:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #003366;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 60px 15px;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary py-3">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="#">
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Sherubtse Logo" width="30" height="30" class="d-inline-block align-text-top me-2">
      Sherubtse College Feedback System
    </a>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
      <ul class="navbar-nav me-3">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link active" href="/user/feedback-form">Submit Feedback</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/user/view-feedback">View Feedback</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-logout ms-2">Log Out</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to Sherubtse College Feedback System</h1>
    <p>Provide your valuable feedback to help us improve the course experience.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container section">
    <div class="highlight-box mb-4">
      <h4>Welcome to the Sherubtse College Feedback System</h4>
      <p>
        At Sherubtse College, we value your voice. This platform is designed
        to make it easy and secure for students to share feedback on courses,
        teaching methods, campus facilities, and overall learning experiences.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your input helps us enhance academic quality, support student wellbeing,
        and build a better educational environment for everyone.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><span class="emoji">ðŸ”’</span> Anonymous & Confidential</li>
        <li><span class="emoji">âœ…</span> Used to Improve Teaching & Learning</li>
        <li><span class="emoji">ðŸ”¹</span> Your Voice Matters</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="row text-center mb-4">
      <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <h6>Submit Feedback</h6>
        <p>Share your feedback for the course you've taken this semester</p>
        <a href="/user/feedback-form" class="feature-btn start">Start Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <h6>View Feedback</h6>
        <p>Check what feedback you've submitted so far.</p>
        <a href="/user/view-feedback" class="feature-btn view">View</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
      <h5>Why Give Feedback?</h5>
      <p>
        Your feedback helps improve teaching, learning, and campus life at Sherubtse College.
        It's quick, anonymous, and makes your voice heard.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Improves teaching quality</li>
        <li>Enhances your learning experience</li>
        <li>Helps the college make better decisions</li>
        <li>Promotes open communication</li>
        <li>Keeps your identity private</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Sherubtse College. All rights reserved.<br />
    Contact: info@sherubtse.edu.bt | Phone: +975-123-4567
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
